From 2bb7d3b19c3eeca8b196fe9dc1039ab61ed7e2d7 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Friedemann Kleint <Friedemann.Kleint@qt.io>
Date: Wed, 25 Mar 2026 15:08:50 +0100
Subject: shiboken6_generator: Change class CodeModel into a non-instantiable
 Q_GADGET

CodeModel aggregated a global namespace item and some file items which
were not actually used. Disable instantiation and remove the unused
parts. Remove the code model instance from the node constructors
and simplify the code accordingly. Also remove the node kind default
parameter and provided by the macro DECLARE_MODEL_NODE and remove
it entirely on this occasion. Repack the node classes' members.

Task-number: PYSIDE-3286
Change-Id: I643bab524adfee897eea840480623df84f22ff5f
Reviewed-by: Cristian Maureira-Fredes <cristian.maureira-fredes@qt.io>
(cherry picked from commit dbb6d8fab77e4ab1250da4f152a147b1fdcdc5d3)
Reviewed-by: Qt Cherry-pick Bot <cherrypick_bot@qt-project.org>
